videos.headline: Florida strikes first on Pitts' TD
videos.description: Kyle Trask links up with Kyle Pitts for a five-yard touchdown to put Florida ahead of Towson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida strikes first on Pitts' TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Trask calls his own number for Florida TD
videos.description: Kyle Trask runs it up the gut for a Gators' one-yard touchdown to increase their lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trask calls his own number for Florida TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Florida's Pitts rises for his 2nd TD grab
videos.description: Kyle Trask looks for Kyle Pitts in the end zone and the Gators TE elevates to make a nice seven-yard touchdown.
